"make allcoq" compiles all coq files in coq_src

"make alldoc" compiles all the documentations from coq files in
coq_src, the pdf docs are in coq_src/pdf, the html docs are in
coq_src/html.

See details about the generation of the makefile in
coq_src/resources/README.

Source pour la preuve de comlplétude de la déduction naturelle au premier ordre:
https://lig-membres.imag.fr/michel.levy/ENSEIGNEMENT/INF242_2008_2009/cours2007.pdf